🎈题目：
输入：
Customers table:
+----+-------+
| id | name  |
+----+-------+
| 1  | Joe   |
| 2  | Henry |
| 3  | Sam   |
| 4  | Max   |
+----+-------+
Orders table:
+----+------------+
| id | customerId |
+----+------------+
| 1  | 3          |
| 2  | 1          |
+----+------------+
输出：
+-----------+
| Customers |
+-----------+
| Henry     |
| Max       |
+-----------+

🎈答案：
select name as Customers
from Customers
where Customers.id not in (select customerId from Orders)
